      "text": "America is reindustrializing and there are few better examples than First Solar's Perrysburg, Ohio, manufacturing and R&D campus, which @RepRoKhanna, Ranking Member of @ChinaSelect, and @RepMarcyKaptur of Ohio visited on Saturday. What they saw: American workers building world-class technology, American families benefiting from good-paying jobs, and proof that American manufacturers, backed by American supply chains, can go toe-to-toe with China on a level playing field and compete to win. Their reactions say it all: 📽️\n\n#MadeInAmerica #AmericanJobs #AmericanManufacturing #FirstSolar \n#AmericasSolarCompany #Reindustrialize\n\n@CmteOnCCPDems",
